  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study investigating the influence of fat distribution, genetic susceptibility markers for
      type 2 diabetes (T2DM) and fat distribution, epigenetic and transcriptomic changes and gut
      hormone responses to a mixed meal on diabetes remission following bariatric surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
